---
import "@/styles/global.css";
import "@/styles/partners.css";
import "@/styles/about/faq.css";
import Button from "@/components/Button.astro"
import Navigation from "@/components/Navigation.astro";
import Footer from "@/components/Footer.astro";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta name="description" content="QUT AI & ML Society FAQ Page" />
    <title>QUT AI & ML Society</title>
  </head>

  <body class="background-dots">
    <Navigation />

    <div class="content-wrapper top-space vacant-space">
      <!-- FAQ HEADER -->
      <section class="pink-panel">
        <p class="pink-title">Frequently Asked Questions</p>
      </section>

      <div class="info-panel-wrapper">

        <section class="info-panel">
          <h3>What is the QUT AI & ML Society?</h3>
          <p>
            The QUT AI & ML Society is a student‑led group at Queensland University of Technology focused on artificial intelligence and machine learning. The society supports learning through hands‑on workshops, collaborative projects, networking events, and talks with industry professionals. Members range from beginners curious about AI to students working on portfolios and real‑world machine learning applications.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="info-panel">
          <h3>Who can join?</h3>
          <p>
            Any QUT student with an interest in AI, data science, machine learning, or related technology can join. The society welcomes students from all disciplines and skill levels who want to learn, build projects, and grow their technical skills.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="info-panel">
          <h3>How do I become a member?</h3>
          <p>
            If you’re a QUT student interested in AI, machine learning, or data science, becoming a member of the QUT AI & ML Society is easy. Memberships can be found 
            <a 
              href="https://campus.hellorubric.com/?tab=memberships&s=11397" 
              class="link-primary" 
              target="_blank" 
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >here</a>. 
            Once you join, you’ll gain access to all of our events, workshops, project nights, and networking opportunities with industry professionals and fellow students.  
            Members are also invited to participate in collaborative projects, receive updates about upcoming competitions, and get early access to exclusive society initiatives.  
            Don’t forget to also join our Discord server and follow our Instagram page to stay connected and up to date with all society news.
          </p>
        </section>


        <section class="info-panel">
          <h3>What activities and events does the society run?</h3>
          <p>
            The QUT AI & ML Society hosts a range of events including project-nights, industry talks, networking nights, welcome events, project nights, and collaborative build sessions. These are designed to help members learn core tools and techniques in AI and machine learning and connect with peers and professionals in tech.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="info-panel">
          <h3>How can I volunteer or help with events?</h3>
          <p>
            Members can volunteer by helping organise workshops, supporting project nights, mentoring peers, or assisting with social media and community outreach. The society often announces these opportunities through Discord and their social pages.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="info-panel">
          <h3>How do I become a sponsor or industry partner?</h3>
          <p>
            Businesses and professionals interested in supporting the QUT AI & ML Society can reach out to the society’s team via their website or social media to discuss partnership opportunities. Sponsors often contribute through guest talks, mentorship, event support, and industry‑linked workshops.
          </p>
        </section>


        <section class="info-panel">
          <h3>Where can I find more information?</h3>
          <p>
            Visit the society’s official website: 
            <a 
              href="https://discord.gg/CqkUzVVkXX" 
              class="link-primary" 
              target="_blank" 
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >Discord</a>, 
            <a 
              href="https://github.com/qut-aiml" 
              class="link-primary" 
              target="_blank" 
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >GitHub</a>, 
            <a 
              href="https://www.instagram.com/qut_aiml/" 
              class="link-primary" 
              target="_blank" 
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >Instagram</a>, 
            <a 
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/qut-aiml/" 
              class="link-primary" 
              target="_blank" 
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >LinkedIn</a> 
          for the latest updates, event details, and ways to join or collaborate.
          </p>
        </section>


      </div>
    </div>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
